item.title: CVE-2024-9423|2024-10-02T15:36:16.885Z -- hp%20inc. -- certain%20hp%20laserjet%20printers
item.description: Certain HP LaserJet printers may potentially experience a denial of service when a user sends a raw JPEG file to the printer. The printer displays a “JPEG Unsupported” message which may not clear, potentially blocking queued print jobs.
